org.reflections
Class ReflectionUtils

java.lang.Object
  org.reflections.ReflectionUtils
Direct Known Subclasses:
Reflections
public abstract class ReflectionUtils
extends Object

convenient reflection methods

some helper methods to get superTypes, methods, fields matching some predicates, generally: 

     Set<?> result = getAllXXX(type/s, withYYY)
     Set<?> result = getAllXXX(type/s, Predicates.and(withYYY, withZZZ))
see getAllSuperTypes(Class, com.google.common.base.Predicate), getAllFields(Class, com.google.common.base.Predicate), getAllMethods(Iterable, com.google.common.base.Predicate), getAll(Iterable, com.google.common.base.Predicate)

predicates included here all starts with "with", for example withAnnotation(java.lang.annotation.Annotation), withModifier(int), withParametersAssignableFrom(Class[])

              withPrefix("get"),
              withParametersCount(0)));
